headline: AJ Bell Selects Northern Trust and Carne Group to Support Its In-House Fund Range
summary: LONDON, November 24, 2025--Northern Trust (Nasdaq: NTRS) and Carne Group (Carne) announce they are providing asset servicing and Authorised Corporate Director services respectively for AJ Bell, a United Kingdom (UK)-based asset manager and one of the country’s leading investment platforms.
